  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to investigate the influence of several anti-diabetic
      regimens (metformin,glitazone,sulfonylurea,glinidine) and diet on metabolic parameters in
      patients with recently diagnosed type 2 diabetes.
    </textblock>
